0.4.1: 
        Allow lcdd to run as client
        Fix some special characters


0.4:  Change network protocol to TCP
	Add support for user scroll and blink
	Add C++ class to the library
	Add autoconf support
	WARNING: Not backward compatible!

0.3:	Client also works without server
	Created lcd library (static and shared)
	Server can be polled (ping->pong)
	Can ask to server contents of both lines

0.2: 	Various bugfixes
	-Short strings not doubled anymore
	-No more "outofbounds" on substr
	-Long date/time screen by default

0.1: 	First release
